ActJobs, Growth and Long-term Prosperity Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on which this Order is published and six months after that Day as the Days on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder (1) fixing the day on which the Order is published in the Canada Gazette, Part II, as the day on which section 413 and subsection 414(1) of the JOBS, GROWTH AND LONG-TERM PROSPERITY ACT, chapter 19 of the Statutes of Canada, 2012, COME INTO FORCE; and (2) fixing the day that is six months after the day on which the Order is published in the Canada Gazette, Part II, as the day on which section 418 of the same Act COMES INTO FORCE.
